Package population

Population package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to store and implement the evolution of individuals throughout a stochastic simulation as well as a Comparator implementations to sort any kind of List from the JDK library.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IIndividual
    IIndividual.java - An interface outlining the minimum required methods to be provided by an individual
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Individual
    Individual.java - A class defining the attributes of each individual and how it evolves throughout the simulation, according to the project parameters
    IndividualComparator
    IndividualComparator.java - A class implementing the Generic Comparator class, exclusively to compare Individuals by their current comfort.

Package population Description
